This repository contains open-source software (OSS) and follows the
[REUSE specification v3.0][reuse-specification] for stating license information.

All source files in this repository will either contain copyright and
[SPDX ID][spdx-id] information in their headers or `*.license` files next to
them, but never the original license texts.

The license texts for the OSS contained in this repository are kept
at the top-level directory `LICENSES/`, named with their SPDX IDs.
No copyrights are contained in these files, instead refer to
the individual source files.

The license that should be used by default for new source files in this
repository is the
[GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1 or later][lgpl-21-license].

Please refer to the [SPDX License List][spdx-licenses] for more
information about each SPDX ID.

[reuse-specification]: https://reuse.software/spec/
[spdx-licenses]: https://spdx.org/licenses
[spdx-id]: https://spdx.org/ids
[lgpl-21-license]: LICENSES/LGPL-2.1-or-later.txt
